			<h1>{{page-title}}</h1>

			<p>Kiva relies on grants from foundations, corporations and individuals to expand our impact, reach new audiences and test innovative ideas that push the boundaries of microfinance. Our key supporters provide us with generous financial and organizational support. They also raise awareness of our mission and help further our goal of connecting people through lending to alleviate poverty. Below are a few of our key strategic programs in need of support. Contact us at <a href="mailto:development@kiva.org">development@kiva.org</a> to learn more.</p>

