					<p><img data-interchange="[//www-kiva-org.global.ssl.fastly.net/cms/page/images/kiva-labs-std.jpg, (default)],[//www-kiva-org.global.ssl.fastly.net/cms/page/images/kiva-labs-retina.jpg, (retina)]"></p>
